Far away from where he lived

He was heading for the coast

Billy, all the world is waiting for you
Everybody's talking about Billy

He was sitting on a beach
And he met a girl named Suzie

Billy wrote her poems

And once Suzie had gone back home
Billy's peaches all were rotten
Billy's nights were spent alone

Billy what are you going to do?

They had similar objectives
Yeah their partnership made sense

William went along one Monday night

William nodded along silently
He long ago gave up on finding joy in anything

His wife was gonna leave him soon

Each new classroom was the same
